{"tid":1813660,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[強國崛起] Geekbench 公佈「跑分作弊清單」，全部7部為中國品牌手機，其中6部係華為","createTime":"2020-01-06T12:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T01:29:22.000Z","uid":155095,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b37600e67b4e94c0a5f66419cb5a36dfb79c9e","tid":1813660,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/39148/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F39148%2F&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=89e72a0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F39148%2F&h=777ae58b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://3c.ltn.com.tw/news/39148/</a><br />\n<br />\n知名跑分平台 <strong>Geekbench</strong> 稍早更新了一個「作弊」清單，認定有 7 款手機在執行 Geekbench 時，會切換到一個獨立的模式來進行跑分、提高分數，以展現與現實體驗不同的更佳成果。<br />\n<br />\n具體來說，其手法主要是不正常地暫時調高 CPU 時脈以衝刺效能，不過因這樣的頻率若放到日常使用，可能會造成手機發熱或大幅降低續航，因此用戶的手機平時並不會以這個頻率來運作。<br />\n<br />\nGeekbench 同時質疑，這幾款手機在其他跑分測試中，也可能有同樣的情形。<br />\n至於本次被列入<span style=\"color: red;\">「作弊」榜單中，則全數是中國品牌</span>，同時以<span style=\"color: red;\">華為佔了 6 支最多</span>，另一款則由 OnePlus 拿下。其詳細名單則包括：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1、Mate10<br />\n2、Mate10 Pro<br />\n3、P20<br />\n4、P20 Pro<br />\n5、榮耀Play<br />\n6、Mate 30 Pro 5G 版<br />\n7、OnePlus 5</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/542413/original/cda51be5850d3d9df77f163ee96f282e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F542413%2Foriginal%2Fcda51be5850d3d9df77f163ee96f282e.jpg&h=9b7285fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別的是，華為的 P20、P20 Pro 和榮耀Play，在前年也曾被另一測試工具 <strong>3DMark</strong> 點名作弊。其開發商 UL 並指出，3DMark 共有兩個版本，分別為開放版本和內部測試版，但在內倍測試版中或許因華為手機無法辨識 3DMark 的名字，最後跑出了遠比開放版低的成績。<br />\n<br />\n目前，被點名作弊的手機，也都無法在 Geekbench 和 3DMark 上查詢分數。"},{"pid":"53adc8585f7bbbc164b567835f308d7aae0b143a","tid":1813660,"uid":9142,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"不意外"},{"pid":"cfe320e9b812a06665c0cf2ae9c3ca20f90982d8","tid":1813660,"uid":46720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:30:56.000Z","msg":"芝麻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164ff367c816c5199e3dc0ad32c53fa2e2084771","tid":1813660,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:32:24.000Z","msg":"實例2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[為所欲為] 華為mate30被指動態降低遊戲解析度，遊戲性能測試數據全部作廢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"be23ee811552cfb67e8f1cb8ff105a86581c3d08","tid":1813660,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:46:58.000Z","msg":"揚威國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b304914215bcfff1ce183fd69595d6fc8db65f2","tid":1813660,"uid":168730,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S0JS6HQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS0JS6HQ.jpg&h=ab8ef33d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09cb855c2c86c6ab0403b2e1e8bc23fc5f52feee","tid":1813660,"uid":34550,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"Published Sep 10, 2018 by John Poole<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.geekbench.com/blog/2018/09/huawei-benchmark-boost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.geekbench.com%2Fblog%2F2018%2F09%2Fhuawei-benchmark-boost%2F&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=07e06dca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.geekbench.com/blog/2018/09/huawei-benchmark-boost/</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年既新聞而家先拎黎講<im